"'''Gottu and His Vibro-ax'''" is a short story written by [[Bill Slavicsek]], originally published in the ''[[Dark Force Rising Sourcebook]]'' as "Gottu and His Vibroaxe." It was reprinted with the alternate spelling for [[Vibro-ax/Legends|vibro-ax]] in [[1996]]'s ''[[The Thrawn Trilogy Sourcebook]]'' and later archived on [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]].

